N2  - In this article the author discusses why management researchers around the globe should want to be published in the ?Academy of Management Journal.? He examines the growing international community that reads the journal and notes that it is seen as one of the top management journals in the world. He also discusses the rigorous review process that articles are subjected to, illustrating how difficult it is to be published in the journal and what type of honor that bestows upon the author.
